14:05.100 --> 14:06.722
- What are you doing?

14:06.822 --> 14:09.046
- Ah! Hey, sweetie.
- Ah.

14:09.146 --> 14:10.448
- Remember how I was vacuuming
in the kitchen,

14:10.548 --> 14:11.729
the dining room,

14:11.829 --> 14:13.492
and then under our bed
and under your bed

14:13.592 --> 14:16.095
