18:15.366 --> 18:19.152
- It's just, I was looking
forward to some stability.

18:19.252 --> 18:20.393
I guess that's gone.

18:20.493 --> 18:22.116
- Listen, we're gonna
be okay, okay?

18:22.216 --> 18:23.918
We're gonna work
through this together.

18:24.018 --> 18:25.560
You're gonna finally finish
that novel,

18:25.660 --> 18:28.264
and in the meantime,
I'm gonna go back to work.

18:29.906 --> 18:32.330
- Really? Are you sure?

18:32.430 --> 18:35.174
- Yes. You know,
investigating Sofía

18:35.274 --> 18:38.578
made me realise
I really miss practicing law.

18:38.678 --> 18:40.942
And hey, at least now
you can wear that--that watch.

18:41.042 --> 18:43.044
- Oh, yeah.

18:44.486 --> 18:46.710
Ooh, it's cold.

18:46.810 --> 18:49.313
But you know what?
Feels good.

18:49.413 --> 18:54.601
Watch bought with lies is
now a watch of...righteousness.

18:54.701 --> 18:57.925
- No more telltale ticking.
I can't hear it at all.

18:58.025 --> 19:00.028
- Me neither.

19:00.629 --> 19:02.652
