Cold broke it.

19:02.752 --> 19:04.754
I think I'm gonna bring this
back to Connor's watch guy.

19:07.238 --> 19:10.663
- Hey.
- Hey.

19:10.763 --> 19:13.346
- Sorry, I--I think I left
my clip-on ring light here.

19:13.446 --> 19:15.790
- Don't you have, like,
five of those?

19:15.890 --> 19:17.632
- I guess.
