to kiss you.

20:20.780 --> 20:22.782
- Oh.

20:25.386 --> 20:26.367
I'm starting to think
this thing

20:26.467 --> 20:27.850
might actually be a thing.

20:27.950 --> 20:31.895
- Oh, it's definitely a thing.
- Mm-hmm.

20:31.995 --> 20:35.520
- But let's just keep it
between us for now.

20:37.202 --> 20:39.626
