20:51.525 --> 20:52.626
- So what do you say
to your fans

20:52.726 --> 20:55.028
who feel like you've lied
to them

20:55.128 --> 20:57.071
about your entire life?

20:57.171 --> 21:00.796
- Well, uh, I would say
I am so sorry.

21:00.896 --> 21:03.479
And then I would say
thank God.

21:03.579 --> 21:05.082
- Thank God?

21:05.182 --> 21:07.565
- Yes, because now
I am able to--you know,

21:07.665 --> 21:09.808
to--to embrace my truth

21:09.908 --> 21:11.811
and tell them my real story.

21:11.911 --> 21:14.054
And I'm gonna expose it all
in my new book.

21:14.154 --> 21:16.497
And I'm writing it
with Michael Chabon.

21:16.597 --> 21:17.779
- [groans]
- I can't wait to read it.

21:17.879 --> 21:19.101
- Chabon.

21:19.201 --> 21:20.904
- To think I liked her flan.

21:21.004 --> 21:22.306
- It's gonna be amazing.

21:22.406 --> 21:24.408
[laughter]
